		**Abstract****: **Surface maintenance and   inspection of    large structures is important to increase service life and efficiency. But the manual methods have their short-comings like limited maneuverability, risk of accidents errors in inspection etc. This project aims at developing a magnetic wheel that can be used in a climbing robot to climb large   steel structures. The research is directed at designing light-weight magnet system to provide optimum adhesion force.

