	- **RESULTS AND PROJECT OUTCOME**

Design for a magnetic wheel was generated based on the research and the magnetic pull force calculations. The outcomes and the benefits of this projects are:

- A more enhanced design than the earlier wheel, a greater load bearing capacity than the earlier design in the same size.

- The generation of the Magnetic pull force calculator will help the user to simulate the magnetic pull force by varying the required parameters and carrying out some permutations and combinations.

- The table that was created in excel along with the graph of pull force versus diameter of wheel will help the user to pick out the predefined dimensions of the wheels and magnet according to his/her requirement of the payload.

- The design of the Halbach cylinder uses square magnets which are readily available in the market.

- Producing the magnetic wheel in-house rather than outsourcing it will reduce the cost and also will allow the user with large customization according to the requirements.

